!******************************************************************************
!* MACROS :     <none>  only direct execution calls.
!********************************************************
! Global variables must exist before menu is displayed:
!            mmcMenuEnable      = 0 for offline
!                               = 1 for online
!            mmcMenuEnableFS    = 0 for fast scan
!                               = 1 for normal scan
!            MSTuneTraceState   = 1 (default) for tracing off
!                               = 3 for tracing on
!            MSManCalOpenF      = 0 for file open for data acq in tune
!                                 1 (default) no file open yet for data acq in tune 
!            MSManCalCloseF     = 0 (default) for no file open yet for data acq in tune
!                                 1 for file open for data acq in tune
!            MSToggleScanState =  1 (default) normal data
!                                 3 filtered raw data
!            MSManShow          = 0 No Atune.Reg exists, disable single polarity
!                                   Autotunes
!                                 1 Atune.Reg exists, enable single polarity
!                                   Autotunes
!
!*  Defines Manual MSD Calibration base menus
!
! =========================================================================
! 09/09/99 YD  Removed Printer Setup item from the menu.
! 06/07/01 PHC Added dynamic ramping items for G1946D with Lens2RF.
! 06/2002  PHC Added Fast Scan options. Removed "Edit Autotune Spray Chamber
!              Parameters"item from the menu.
! 11/29/05 LL  Added Globalization changes.
! 02/10/06 CPL Updated macro header information
! 03/16/06 CPL Disable "Check Gain Calibration" in Fast Scan mode.
! 06/04/19 ueff Ultra Fast Scan labels for menu item for G6140A
! 07/01/08 CPL Add "Reset Gain Calibration to Defaults" menu item.
! =========================================================================


!*********************************************************************!
